WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Know your numbers. They tell the story a single day can't.

00:06.000 --> 00:11.000
Two numbers matter most.

00:11.000 --> 00:21.000
A1C — your average blood sugar over about three months. One number; the big picture.

00:21.000 --> 00:31.000
Time in range. If you wear a CGM, it's the share of the day you're in target — the picture A1C can't show.

00:31.000 --> 00:38.000
Many adults aim for an A1C around seven percent. But your number is yours. Your care team sets it.

00:38.000 --> 00:49.000
Do this tomorrow. Write down your last A1C and its date. Ask your care team your target. Bring both numbers to every visit.

00:49.000 --> 00:58.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:58.000 --> 01:05.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
